<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Hadmar von Absberg, Pfleger zu Monheim</head><p>Der Rat teilt mit, dass er Friedrich Zesel, Bürger zu Nürnberg, angewiesen hat seine Klage gegen zwei namens Stöklein wegen Nötigung vor dem Landgericht zurückzunehmen.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_232" id="115v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_232_r2l22">Hadmar <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Abtſperg </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_232_r2l23"><expan>pfleg<ex>er</ex></expan> cʒü Manheim / . </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_232_r2l24"><expan>Lıeb<ex>er</ex></expan> Hadmar / Als Jr vns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>Hanſe<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>Lintn<ex>er</ex>s</expan> vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_232_r2l25"><expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> cʒweyer Stöklein <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> / als die Frıcʒ Cʒeſel <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> / auf das </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_232_r2l26"><expan>Lantger<ex>iht</ex></expan> <expan>gelad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> het / 
<del rend="strikethrough"> Dar </del> Alſo <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvir <expan>denſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>B<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_232_r2l27">darvmb cʒerede geſacʒt / vnd <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> ſprıchet / 
<del rend="strikethrough">daʒ ſie </del> Sie <expan>hind<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Jn an </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_232_r2l28">dem ſeinen / daʒ Jn des not <expan>angange<ex>n</ex></expan> ſeÿ / Doch ſo <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir Jn </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_232_r2l29"><expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>vvılle</expan> daran geweıſet / . daʒ er die klag ab tün vnd cʒü <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_232_r2l30">cʒeit davon <expan>laſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> wil / . vnd wir <expan>getrawe<ex>n</ex></expan> ew wol / Jr weıſet </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_232_r2l31">die <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> daran / daʒ ſie den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> an dem ſeinen <expan>vngehind<ex>er</ex>t</expan> <expan>laſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_232_r2l33">vnd ob er des <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> ew beger / daʒ Jr Jm 
<add><ab facs="#facs_232_r2l32">dann </ab></add> von Jn ſlewniges <expan>recht<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_232_r2l34">beholffen ſeit / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>vts<ex>upra</ex></expan> . </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_232" id="115v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Hadmar <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Abtsperg, <expan>pfleg<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        czü Manheim</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan> Hadmar, als ir uns
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt
                                <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Hanse<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Lintn<ex>er</ex>s</expan> und <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> czweyer
                        stöklein <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, als die Fricz Czesel,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, auf das <expan>lantger<ex>iht</ex></expan>
<expan>gelad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> het. Also <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                                <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>b<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex></expan> darumb czerede gesaczt und
                                <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> sprichet, sie
                            <expan>hind<ex>er</ex>n</expan> in an dem seinen, daz in des not
                                <expan>angange<ex>n</ex></expan> sey, doch so
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir in <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille</expan> daran geweiset, daz er die klag ab tün und czü
                                <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> czeit davon
                            <expan>lasse<ex>n</ex></expan> wil. Und wir
                            <expan>getrawe<ex>n</ex></expan> ew wol, ir weiset die
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> daran, daz sie den
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> an dem seinen
                                <expan>ungehind<ex>er</ex>t</expan>
<expan>lasse<ex>n</ex></expan>, und ob er des <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> ew
                        beger, daz ir im <add>dann</add> von in slewniges
                            <expan>recht<ex>e</ex>n</expan> beholffen seit.
                            <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>ut s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
